1. Introduction
------------------------

Welcome to Wifi::Manage,a quick tool for switchin wifi configuration in Perl.

2. Prerequisites
------------------------

Wifi::Manage requires ifconfig,iwconfig,route.

3. Installation
________________________

Do this, in the following order:

        perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make install

